<div class="card card-custom gutter-b cb-card">
    <div class="card-header border-0 pt-6">
        <div class="card-title">
            <div>
                <h3 class="card-label font-weight-bolder mb-1">Backtest parametreleri</h3>
                <div class="text-muted font-size-sm">Bu form Paper Trading değil, yalnızca geçmiş veri testi senaryosunu tanımlar. Gerçek veri/motor sonraki fazda bağlanacaktır.</div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="card-body pt-2">
        <div class="cb-rule-setting-item">
            <div class="cb-rule-setting-header">
                <strong>Strateji ve piyasa bağlamı</strong>
                <span class="cb-badge cb-badge-info" id="cb_backtest_mode_badge">Spot context</span>
            </div>
            <div class="row mt-4">
                <div class="col-12">
                    <label class="cb-form-label">Strateji seçimi</label>
                    <select class="form-control cb-form-control" id="cb_backtest_strategy">
                        <option>EMA Cross Strategy</option>
                        <option>RSI Reversal</option>
                        <option>Breakout Template</option>
                        <option>DCA Template</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6 mt-4">
                    <label class="cb-form-label">Market tipi</label>
                    <select class="form-control cb-form-control" id="cb_backtest_market">
                        <option value="spot">Spot</option>
                        <option value="futures">Futures</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6 mt-4">
                    <label class="cb-form-label">Timeframe</label>
                    <select class="form-control cb-form-control" id="cb_backtest_timeframe">
                        <option>1m</option>
                        <option>5m</option>
                        <option>15m</option>
                        <option selected>1h</option>
                        <option>4h</option>
                        <option>1d</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="cb-rule-setting-item mt-4">
            <div class="cb-rule-setting-header">
                <strong>Tarih aralığı</strong>
                <span class="cb-badge cb-badge-neutral" id="cb_backtest_range_badge">Son 90 gün</span>
            </div>
            <div class="cb-chip-group cb-chip-group-sm mt-3" data-cb-toggle-group>
                <button type="button" class="cb-chip" data-cb-toggle-active data-cb-backtest-range="7d">Son 7 gün</button>
                <button type="button" class="cb-chip" data-cb-toggle-active data-cb-backtest-range="30d">Son 30 gün</button>
                <button type="button" class="cb-chip is-active" data-cb-toggle-active data-cb-backtest-range="90d">Son 90 gün</button>
                <button type="button" class="cb-chip" data-cb-toggle-active data-cb-backtest-range="custom">Özel aralık</button>
            </div>
            <div class="row mt-4" id="cb_backtest_range_inputs">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <label class="cb-form-label">Başlangıç tarihi</label>
                    <input type="date" class="form-control cb-form-control" id="cb_backtest_start" value="2026-01-01" />
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6 mt-4 mt-md-0">
                    <label class="cb-form-label">Bitiş tarihi</label>
                    <input type="date" class="form-control cb-form-control" id="cb_backtest_end" value="2026-03-20" />
                </div>
                <div class="col-12 mt-3">
                    <div class="text-muted font-size-sm" id="cb_backtest_range_help">Daha uzun aralık, istatistiklerin güvenilirliğini artırır. Kısa aralıklar sonucu olduğundan parlak gösterebilir.</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="cb-rule-setting-item mt-4">
            <div class="cb-rule-setting-header">
                <strong>Sembol ve maliyet varsayımları</strong>
                <span class="cb-badge cb-badge-warning" id="cb_backtest_cost_badge">Fee + slippage etkin</span>
            </div>
            <div class="row mt-4">
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <label class="cb-form-label">Sembol</label>
                    <select class="form-control cb-form-control" id="cb_backtest_symbol">
                        <option>BTCUSDT</option>
                        <option>ETHUSDT</option>
                        <option>SOLUSDT</option>
                        <option>BNBUSDT</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6 mt-4 mt-md-0">
                    <label class="cb-form-label">Başlangıç bakiye</label>
                    <div class="input-group">
                        <div class="input-group-prepend"><span class="input-group-text cb-input-addon">$</span></div>
                        <input type="text" class="form-control cb-form-control" id="cb_backtest_initial_balance" value="10000" />
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6 mt-4">
                    <label class="cb-form-label">Fee</label>
                    <div class="input-group">
                        <input type="text" class="form-control cb-form-control" id="cb_backtest_fee" value="0.10" />
                        <div class="input-group-append"><span class="input-group-text cb-input-addon">%</span></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="cb-helper-text mt-2">İşlem maliyeti sonuçları aşağı çeker; bu alan sonraki fazda gerçek borsa fee yapılarına bağlanabilir.</div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-6 mt-4">
                    <label class="cb-form-label">Slippage</label>
                    <div class="input-group">
                        <input type="text" class="form-control cb-form-control" id="cb_backtest_slippage" value="0.03" />
                        <div class="input-group-append"><span class="input-group-text cb-input-addon">%</span></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="cb-helper-text mt-2">Fiyat kayması varsayımı özellikle düşük timeframe ve agresif stratejilerde sonucu etkileyebilir.</div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="cb-alert cb-alert-warning mt-4 d-none" id="cb_backtest_validation_alert">
            Seçilen tarih aralığı ve maliyet varsayımları sonuç üretmeyi zorlaştırabilir. Bu alan yönlendirici validation foundation olarak hazırlandı.
        </div>

        <div class="cb-toolbar mt-6">
            <button type="button" class="btn btn-primary font-weight-bolder" data-cb-backtest-run>Backtest Başlat <span class="cb-btn-spinner"></span></button>
            <button type="button" class="btn btn-light-primary font-weight-bold" data-cb-backtest-reset>Temizle</button>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
